《'''大城小妞'''》（{{lang-en|''Broad City''}}）是一部於2014年1月22日在[[喜劇中心|喜劇中心]]開播的[[美國|美國]][[喜劇|喜劇]]。<ref name="thefutoncritic1">{{cite web |url=http://www.thefutoncritic.com/news/2013/12/10/abbi-jacobson-and-ilana-glazers-broad-city-comes-to-comedy-central-on-wednesday-january-22-at-1030-pm-et-pt-437014/20131210comedycentral01/ |title=Breaking News - Abbi Jacobson and Ilana Glazer's "Broad City" Comes to Comedy Central(R) on Wednesday, January 22 at 10:30 P.M. ET/PT |publisher=The Futon Critic |date=2013-12-10 |accessdate=2014-01-31 |archive-date=2014-01-31 |archive-url=https://archive.today/20140131010702/http://www.thefutoncritic.com/news/2013/12/10/abbi-jacobson-and-ilana-glazers-broad-city-comes-to-comedy-central-on-wednesday-january-22-at-1030-pm-et-pt-437014/20131210comedycentral01/ |dead-url=no }}</ref>

本劇由[[艾拉娜·格雷澤|艾拉娜·格雷澤]]與[[艾比·雅各森|艾比·雅各森]]開創並擔任主演，在2009年至2011年期間，兩人開創了與本劇同名的網路劇。<ref name="AV Club S01E01 review">{{cite web |title=Broad City: 'What A Wonderful World' |url=http://www.avclub.com/review/what-a-wonderful-world-107188 |website=[[影音俱樂部|影音俱樂部]] |first=Caroline |last=Framke |date=2014-01-22 |accessdate=2014-01-30 |archive-date=2014-01-30 |archive-url=https://archive.today/20140130192911/http://www.avclub.com/review/what-a-wonderful-world-107188 |dead-url=no }}</ref>

2015年1月14日宣布續訂第3季。<ref>{{cite news|last1=Dockterman|first1=Eliana|title=Broad City Renewed for Season 3|url=http://time.com/3667432/broad-city-renewed/|website=[[時代_(雜誌)|時代雜誌]]|publisher=[[時代_(雜誌)|時代雜誌]]|accessdate=2015-01-14|date=2015-01-14|archive-date=2015-01-18|archive-url=https://archive.today/20150118140858/http://time.com/3667432/broad-city-renewed/|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.vulture.com/2015/11/broad-city-sets-third-season-premiere-date.html#|title=Guess When Broad City Comes Back for Its Third Season? Come On, Please, Just Guess|publisher=Vulture.com|first=Jesse David|last=Fox|date=2015-11-19|accessdate=2015-11-19|archive-date=2015-12-25|archive-url=https://archive.today/20151225153424/http://www.vulture.com/2015/11/broad-city-sets-third-season-premiere-date.html%23|dead-url=no}}</ref>2016年1月6日，喜劇中心提前宣布續訂第4季與第5季。<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.hollywoodreporter.com/live-feed/comedy-central-renews-broad-city-852532|title=Comedy Central Renews 'Broad City' for Season 4 and 5; Orders Pot Comedy|publisher=[[荷里活報道|好萊塢報導]]|first=Lacey|last=Rose|date=2016-01-06|accessdate=2016-01-06|archive-date=2021-01-26|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210126125259/https://www.hollywoodreporter.com/live-feed/comedy-central-renews-broad-city-852532|dead-url=no}}</ref>2018年4月12日，證實第5季將為本劇最終季。<ref>{{cite web|url=http://deadline.com/2018/04/broad-city-end-five-seasons-final-season-ilana-glazer-abbi-jacobson-first-look-deal-comedy-central-1202362030/|title=‘Broad City’ To End After Season 5, Ilana Glazer & Abbi Jacobson Ink First-Look Deal With Comedy Central|publisher=[[Deadline.com|Deadline.com]]|first=Nellie|last=Andreeva|date=2018-04-12|accessdate=2018-04-12|archive-date=2021-02-11|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210211165714/https://deadline.com/2018/04/broad-city-end-five-seasons-final-season-ilana-glazer-abbi-jacobson-first-look-deal-comedy-central-1202362030/|dead-url=no}}</ref>

== 故事 ==
講述2個[[猶太裔|猶太裔]]閨蜜艾拉娜與艾比互相扶持，並努力在[[紐約市|紐約市]]生存的故事。

