== 製作 ==
[[艾拉娜·格雷澤|艾拉娜·格雷澤]]與[[艾比·雅各森|艾比·雅各森]]都於{{link-en|Upright Citizens Brigade|Upright Citizens Brigade}}參加課程並因此相識。2010年2月，她們開始在[[YouTube|YouTube]]上開發她們的網路劇，並廣受歡迎，也因此受到[[艾米·波勒|艾米·波勒]]的注意，並在開發電視版本時，擔任了本劇的執行製作。在格雷澤與雅各森為試播集創作劇本時，兩位女主角姓名最初設定為艾芙琳·維斯勒（{{lang|en|Evelyn Wexler}}）與卡莉·艾布雷姆斯（{{lang|en|Carly Abrams}}），<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.tv-calling.com/scripts/TV_Comedies/Broad_City_1x01.pdf|title=Pilot episode script|accessdate=2015-08-09|archive-date=2016-03-04|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160304220118/http://www.tv-calling.com/scripts/TV_Comedies/Broad_City_1x01.pdf|dead-url=no}}</ref>但最後改為兩人的真實名字。

== 評價 ==
=== 評論家評論 ===
於[[Metacritic|Metacritic]]整合的評論中，第1季獲得75分（滿分100分；14位評論家），收到普遍的好評。<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.metacritic.com/tv/broad-city|title=Broad City - Season 1 Reviews|publisher=[[Metacritic|Metacritic]]|accessdate=2014-01-30|archive-date=2015-08-09|archive-url=https://archive.today/20150809173156/http://www.metacritic.com/tv/broad-city|dead-url=no}}</ref>於[[爛番茄|爛番茄]]整合的評論中，第1季獲得96%的新鮮度、8.0/10分（23位評論家），評論家共識：「由有才華的製作人創造出巧妙的劇本及卓越的路線，使《大城小紐》有著別樣的風味。」<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.rottentomatoes.com/tv/broad-city/s01/|title=Broad City: Season 1|date=2014-01-22|work=爛番茄|accessdate=2015-02-21|archive-date=2016-05-23|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160523071517/http://www.rottentomatoes.com/tv/broad-city/s01|dead-url=no}}</ref>[[影音俱樂部|影音俱樂部]]將第一季列名為2014年最佳電視節目中。<ref name="AV Club best TV shows 2014">{{cite web|title=The best TV shows of 2014 (part 2)|url=http://www.avclub.com/article/best-tv-shows-2014-part-2-212571|website=[[影音俱樂部|影音俱樂部]]|first=|last=|date=2014-12-11|accessdate=2015-01-10|archive-date=2014-12-11|archive-url=https://archive.today/20141211063004/http://www.avclub.com/article/best-tv-shows-2014-part-2-212571|dead-url=no}}</ref>

[[華爾街日報|華爾街日報]]稱本劇為「女性主義的逆襲」，評論家梅根·安傑洛（{{lang|en|Megan Angelo}}）引用主演艾拉娜·格雷澤所說的話：「如果你只看一集我們的節目，並不會帶給你太多的訊息，但如果你看完全集，我想，這很鼓勵女性。」<ref name="Angelo 2011">{{cite news|last=Angelo|first=Megan|title=The Sneak-Attack Feminism of ‘Broad City’|website=[[華爾街日報|華爾街日報]]|date=2011-02-14|url=http://blogs.wsj.com/speakeasy/2011/02/14/the-sneak-attack-feminism-of-broad-city/|accessdate=2014-07-15|archive-date=2014-03-04|archive-url=https://archive.today/20140304024523/http://blogs.wsj.com/speakeasy/2011/02/14/the-sneak-attack-feminism-of-broad-city/|dead-url=no}}</ref>

[[娛樂周刊|娛樂周刊]]的凱倫·維爾比（{{lang|en|Karen Valby}}）描述本劇「深深的古怪，古怪的窩心，完全爆笑的喜劇。」<ref name="Rotten Tomatoes 2014">{{cite web|title=Broad City: Season 1|website=Rotten Tomatoes|date=2014-03-28|url=http://www.rottentomatoes.com/tv/broad-city/|accessdate=2014-07-15|archive-date=2020-03-07|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200307031928/https://www.rottentomatoes.com/tv/broad-city/|dead-url=no}}</ref>

本劇開播雖只有914000位觀眾，但卻收穫了廣大的好評。<ref name="Jarvey">{{cite news|last=Jarvey|first=Natalie|title='Drunk History,' 'Broad City': Why TV Networks Are Interested in Adapting Online Series Again|website=[[荷里活報道|好萊塢報導]]|url=http://www.hollywoodreporter.com/news/drunk-history-broad-city-why-678901|accessdate=2014-07-15|archive-date=2021-01-26|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210126140945/https://www.hollywoodreporter.com/news/drunk-history-broad-city-why-678901|dead-url=no}}</ref>

本劇第2季的評價更勝第一季，於Metacritic整合的評論中，獲得了89分（滿分100分；8位評論家），屬極佳的讚譽。<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.metacritic.com/tv/broad-city/season-2|title=Broad City - Season 2 Reviews|work=Metacritic|accessdate=2015-02-21|archive-date=2015-01-21|archive-url=https://archive.today/20150121170124/http://www.metacritic.com/tv/broad-city/season-2|dead-url=no}}</ref>於爛番茄整合的評論中，第2季獲得100%新鮮度、9.0/10分（11位評論家）。<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.rottentomatoes.com/tv/broad-city/s02/|title=Broad City: Season 2|date=2015-01-14|work=爛番茄|accessdate=2015-02-21|archive-date=2016-05-02|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160502052700/http://www.rottentomatoes.com/tv/broad-city/s02|dead-url=no}}</ref>

第3季於Metacritic整合的評論中，獲得了87分（滿分100分；8位評論家），屬極佳的讚譽。<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.metacritic.com/tv/broad-city/season-3|title=Broad City - Season 3 Reviews|work=Metacritic|accessdate=2016-07-14|archive-date=2016-07-14|archive-url=https://archive.today/20160714125519/http://www.metacritic.com/tv/broad-city/season-3|dead-url=no}}</ref>於爛番茄整合的評論中，第3季獲得100%新鮮度、9.21/10分（17位評論家）。<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.rottentomatoes.com/tv/broad-city/s03/|title=Broad City: Season 3|date=2015-01-14|work=爛番茄|accessdate=2016-07-14|archive-date=2016-10-21|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20161021072830/https://www.rottentomatoes.com/tv/broad-city/s03/|dead-url=no}}</ref>

第4季於Metacritic整合的評論中，獲得了89分（滿分100分；8位評論家），屬極佳的讚譽。<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.metacritic.com/tv/broad-city/season-4|title=Broad City - Season 4 Reviews|work=Metacritic|accessdate=2017-10-14|archive-date=2020-06-26|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200626085806/https://www.metacritic.com/tv/broad-city/season-4|dead-url=no}}</ref>於爛番茄整合的評論中，第4季獲得100%新鮮度、8.58/10分（9位評論家）。<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.rottentomatoes.com/tv/broad-city/s04/|title=Broad City: Season 4|work=爛番茄|accessdate=2017-10-14}}</ref>

